    <note>Yuan(1) Hong [10367] CHECK Yuan dynasty funerary inscription. At age of 17, he used yin to be director of Zhenjiang fu, Dajun cang. He was made Taishe ling under Zhao(1) Duzong, but Jia(3) Sidao [10374] did not like Mingzhou people and he was purged. After Sidao was disgraced, he was given a temple sinecure and subsequently functional posts. He was offered office under Yuan but use illness as an excuse to decline. Yuan Jue, WJ, 33.2b-6b, 9a-11a (wife, born Shi(5) Diqing, who died in 1266 at age 21, mother of Jue [10286]). CBD, 3, 1853.亦據元人傳記資料索引電子版6128</note>
